Five Easy Steps to Running Your Business 
Most businesses fail within the first two years and it is not for the lack of passion, knowing what to do or 
money. It is from the lack of habit. 
 
Love What You Do...the Money will Follow 
If you are passionate about the things you love, then it comes through in everything that you do. If you are 
passionate about what you are doing, then it is a natural element for the money to follow that path of 
passion. 
 
